# TimeAndDurationBlock(time, duration, isLast)
- ```
{
    "type": "Container",
    "items": [
        ${TimeBlock(time)},
        {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "wrap": true,
            "text": "${duration}",
            "weight": "Lighter",
            "isSubtle": true,
            "spacing": "None"
        }
    ],
    "minHeight": "${if(isLast, '30px', '80px')}",
    "spacing": "None"
}
```

# TimeBlock(time)
- IF: ${contains(toLower(time), 'today')}
    - ```
    {
        "type": "ColumnSet",
        "columns": [
            {
                "type": "Column",
                "items": [
                    {
                        "type": "Image",
                        "url": "${Calendar()}"
                    }
                ],
                "width": "auto"
            },
            {
                "type": "Column",
                "items": [
                    {
                        "type": "TextBlock",
                        "wrap": true,
                        "text": "10:00 PM Today"
                    }
                ],
                "spacing": "Small"
            }
        ]
    }
    ```
- ELSE:
    - ```
    {
        "type": "TextBlock",
        "wrap": true,
        "text": "${time}"
    }
    ```

